lead_paragraph: Joey Carney finally made the decision for himself and told his parents they could no longer try to talk him out of it: As long as he was a match, he would donate part of his liver to his ailing mother and give her a better life. For the long haul.

headline.print_headline: USF Pitcher Carney Donating Part of Liver to Ailing Mother
